@@CPRIEST@@W

Priests are ward-keepers and miracle-callers, trained to outlast chaos through
restoration, sanctification, and relentless holy attrition.

@@CPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wHoly damage@@W bonus from Priest levels
    (+1% per level, up to +100% at 100).
  * @@wHealing throughput@@W bonus
    (+2% per level, up to +200% at 100).

@@CUnique Priest mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wPriest stance@@W (high healing posture).
  * Strongest remort-side baseline scaling for sustained holy healing play.
  * Uses @@wWisdom@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@CPriest reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wPaladin + Priest remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks:
    @@wTwo-Handed@@W, @@wEquip Buckler@@W, and @@wEquip Wand@@W permanently.

